oday\u2019s release were PCE (and core PCE) inflation data that were a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346853640/image_1346853640.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745617-november-2024-personal-income-and-spending", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 18:35:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745176", "title": "Bureau Veritas: The 2028 Targets Make Any Share Price Dip Appealing", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bureau Veritas in the Botlek harbor for auditing and QA controlls at refineries\" data-id=\"1475074031\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andr\u00e9 Muller</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Bureau Veritas (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BVVBY\" title=\"Bureau Veritas SA\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:BVVBY</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BVRDF\" title=\"Bureau Veritas SA\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:BVRDF</a>) is one of the leading companies in the world when it comes to certification and inspection. It has a history of almost 200 years, and during that time frame it has grown its presence</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475074031/image_1475074031.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745176-bureau-veritas-the-2028-targets-make-any-share-price-dip-appealing", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 18:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745597", "title": "Can Walgreens Overcome Its Challenges? (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Walgreens pharmacy\" data-id=\"458331611\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">tupungato</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Since our last Walgreens Boots Alliance (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WBA\" title=\"Walgreens Boots Alliance, Inc.\">WBA</a></span>)<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724353-walgreens-boots-alliance-stock-why-i-sold-my-position\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724353-walgreens-boots-alliance-stock-why-i-sold-my-position\" target=\"_blank\"> coverage, </a>I exited my position to de-risk my portfolio, as I also hold CVS Health (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CVS\" title=\"CVS Health Corporation\">CVS</a>), which presents a stronger risk/reward profile. Last week, WBA saw a temporary jump</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458331611/image_458331611.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745597-can-walgreens-overcome-its-challenges", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 18:25:29", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745594", "title": "Micron Q1 Earnings: Buy This Dip", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"High bandwidth Memory concepts backgrounds. 3d rendering\" data-id=\"2083023796\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mesh cube</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Micron Technology (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a></span>) stock cratered after hours despite reporting record Q1 revenue and 400% YoY growth in data center sales. The market was much more focused on the fiscal Q2 guidance that <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387691-micron-tumbles-weak-q2-forecast-fails-to-overcome-q1-results\">significantly lagged</a> analyst</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2083023796/image_2083023796.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745594-micron-q1-earnings-buy-this-dip", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 18:20:28", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745590", "title": "American Tower: Attractive Yield Following Share Price Slump", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cell phone or mobile service tower in forested area of West Virginia providing broadband service\" data-id=\"1281708700\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4500px\" height=\"2851px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">BackyardProduction</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Article Thesis</h2> <p>American Tower Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMT\" title=\"American Tower Corporation\">AMT</a></span>) is a tower/connectivity real estate investment trust with a solid long-term outlook that has recently come under pressure. Following the share price decline we have seen in recent months, American Tower now offers</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1281708700/image_1281708700.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745590-american-tower-attractive-yield-following-share-price-slump", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 18:14:35", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745589", "title": "Belden: Upsides Now Captured, Margin Of Safety Now Limited", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"New York Stock Exchange, Wall st, New York, USA\" data-id=\"668600179\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8174px\" height=\"5449px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Matteo Colombo</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Update</h2> <p>Following <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4653637-belden-statistical-discount-9x-forward-ebit-11-percent-fcf-yield\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4653637-belden-statistical-discount-9x-forward-ebit-11-percent-fcf-yield\" target=\"_blank\">my last publication</a> on Belden Inc. (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BDC#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BDC#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" target=\"_blank\">BDC</a>) ~12mo ago the stock is +64% after its November '23 selloff, the rally driven ~50% from earnings asset factors and ~50% multiple expansion. I've reviewed the latest developments and revisited the thesis as part of 2025 planning. </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/668600179/image_668600179.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745589-belden-upsides-now-captured-margin-of-safety-now-limited", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 18:10:02", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745609", "title": "BUZZ Investing: Optimism Fuels Continued Rally", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Putting a coin in a white piggy bank at home.\" data-id=\"1363128263\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Guido Mieth</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Strong labor market data, persistent inflation, and investor optimism boosted markets, with Super Micro Computer leading gains amid restored confidence.</em></p> <p>A series of economic and market developments shaped market activity during the recent period between index selection dates (November</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745609-buzz-investing-optimism-fuels-continued-rally", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 18:05:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745608", "title": "Lazard Equity Franchise Portfolio Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1642478364/image_1642478364.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Franchise marketing system in global network connection\" data-id=\"1642478364\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1030px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalph